name: Directionfield
tagline: An Android Direction Field Plotter and Solution Grapher
body:
# DirectionField An Android Direction Field Plotter and Solution Grapher This is a private project. To gain access, please contact Eli Selkin (@eselkin or eselkin@go.pasadena.edu) >A final project for CS3B - Java
>Pasadena City College Fall 2015
>Professor: Jamal Ashraf
This project will be built using Android Studio. The build type is Gradle. Changes should be committed and then pushed regularly. However, a git pull should be done regularly first. Contributors: * Eli Selkin * Chang Zhang * Ahmed Ali * Ben Chen
